        " تَعْجِيلِ اَلطَّوَافِ قَبْلَ اَلْخُرُوجِ إِلَى مِنًى فَقَالَ «هُمَا سَوَاءٌ أَخَّرَ ذَلِكَ أَوْ قَدَّمَهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2778 - Ibn Abi Umayr narrated from Hafs ibn al-Bukhtari, from Abu al-Hasan (as), regarding performing the tawaf early before going to Mina.\nImam (as) said: \"It is the same, whether he delays it or performs it earlier.\""
        ]
